PERMITTED USES
--------------
You MAY use these Assets without additional permission to:

  1. Refer to, link to, or identify Sentrix Chain in editorial content
     (news articles, blog posts, reviews, academic papers, tutorials).

  2. Display the Sentrix Chain logo when integrating with the Sentrix
     Chain network — for example, in wallets, block explorers, dApps,
     SDKs, infrastructure tooling, or analytics platforms that connect
     to Sentrix Chain — provided the logo is used accurately, unmodified,
     and does not imply official endorsement beyond the technical
     integration.

  3. Include the Sentrix Chain logo in token listing submissions to
     exchanges, tokenlists, and aggregators (CoinGecko, CoinMarketCap,
     Uniswap tokenlist, Trust Wallet assets, chainlist.org, etc.).

  4. Use the Assets in community-run projects, educational materials,
     and ecosystem initiatives that clearly identify Sentrix Chain as
     the underlying protocol.

PROHIBITED USES
---------------
You MAY NOT, without explicit written permission from Sentrix Labs:

  1. Modify, recolor, distort, rotate, or create substantially different
     derivative versions of the logo or marks.

  2. Use the Assets in merchandise (clothing, stickers, accessories,
     physical goods) intended for commercial sale.

  3. Use the Assets in a way that implies an official endorsement,
     partnership, investment relationship, or affiliation with
     Sentrix Labs, Sentrix Chain, or the Sentrix ecosystem that does
     not in fact exist.

  4. Register the marks ("Sentrix", "Sentrix Chain", or the logo) as
     a trademark in any jurisdiction.

  5. Use the Assets in connection with illegal activity, adult content,
     hate speech, scams, fraudulent tokens impersonating official Sentrix
     Chain tokens, or anything that would damage the reputation of the
     Sentrix Chain project.

  6. Use the Assets on websites, applications, or tokens that imitate
     official Sentrix Chain products with the intent to deceive users
     (phishing, fake airdrops, impersonation).

